-Credit_-Albert-Trujillo-Effects-By-Ingibjorg-Birgisdottir.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="琼西。图片来源：Albert Trujillo，Ingibjörg Birgisdóttir 的效果" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi.-Credit_-Albert-Trujillo-Effects-By-Ingibjorg-Birgisdottir.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi.-Credit_-Albert-Trujillo-Effects-By-Ingibjorg-Birgisdottir-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi.-Credit_-Albert-Trujillo-Effects-By-Ingibjorg-Birgisdottir-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi.-Credit_-Albert-Trujillo-Effects-By-Ingibjorg-Birgisdottir-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi.-Credit_-Albert-Trujillo-Effects-By-Ingibjorg-Birgisdottir-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi.-Credit_-Albert-Trujillo-Effects-By-Ingibjorg-Birgisdottir-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sigur-ros">Sigur Rós</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jonsi">Jónsi</a>宣布推出新专辑《First Light》，以及两首新单曲《Flicker》和《Cherry Blossom》。看看下面的内容。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jonsi-shiver-review-sigur-ros-2764855">Jónsi – “Shiver”评论：Sigur Rós 主唱在 Robyn 的帮助下放下了头发</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>今天（7 月 19 日）透露，《First Light》将是 Jónsi 继 2021 年 10 月发行的冰岛音乐家《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-sigur-ros-jonsis-dreamy-new-solo-album-obsidian-3083264">Obsidian</a> 》之后的第四张录音室专辑。该专辑将于 8 月 30 日通过健康和福祉音乐提供商 Myndstream 与 Lakeshore Records 合作发行并可<a href="https://jonsi.lnk.to/FirstLight" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。</p><p>为了庆祝这一消息，Jónsi 分享了两首主打单曲“Flicker”和“Cherry Blossom”。这两首印象派管弦乐曲目，《Flicker》都是环境和气氛的，逐渐建立起长笛和鸟鸣的合唱，然后陷入和谐的弦乐结局。而《樱花》则更具冥想性，围绕着平静的钢琴独奏展开。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="闪烁" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oiii_AISFCY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Jónsi 最初开始创作这张专辑作为视频游戏配乐，但它最终演变成一个更大的项目，旨在通过音乐探索和平、希望和联系。</p><p> “在人为的全球动乱和动荡时期为电子游戏创作这首音乐，”琼西说，“我把《第一道曙光》想象成一个短暂的奇幻、夸张的乌托邦世界，在那里，每个人和所有事物都永恒地生活在一起。和平与和谐。选择美丽而不是混乱，选择希望而不是恐惧，我们普遍的神圣天使守护者守护着我们，并通过爱、旋律和音乐将我们所有人连为一体。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="樱花" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/II2PLleDE-0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>粉丝们可以期待不久后将发布两首名为“Forest Trill”（其中将包含更多鸟鸣声）和“Undercurrent”的新单曲。</p><p>请查看下面“First Light”的完整专辑曲目列表和艺术作品。</p><h3> <strong>“First Light”曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1. 闪烁</strong><br /><strong>2. 第一缕曙光</strong><br /><strong>3. 绿色草地</strong><br /><strong>4. 清算</strong><br /><strong>5. 樱花</strong><br /><strong>6. 一览众山小</strong><br /><strong>7.一厢情愿的想法</strong><br /><strong>8. 森林颤音</strong><br /><strong>9. 暗流</strong><br /><strong>10. 柳树</strong><br /><strong>11. 寂静</strong><br /><strong>12. 小花</strong><br /><strong>13. 越过栅栏</strong><br /><strong>14. 颤抖</strong></p><figure id="attachment_3776525" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3776525" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3776525" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi-First-Light-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS.jpg" alt="Jónsi 《First Light》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi-First-Light-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi-First-Light-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi-First-Light-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi-First-Light-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi-First-Light-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi-First-Light-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Jonsi-First-Light-album-artwork.-Credit_-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3776525" class="wp-caption-text"> Jónsi 《First Light》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>到目前为止，似乎还没有特色艺术家，不像 Jónsi 的 2020 年专辑“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jonsi-shiver-review-sigur-ros-2764855">Shiver</a> ”，他与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ROBYN">Robyn</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cocteau-TWINS">Cocteau Twins</a>的 Liz Fraser 和制作人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/AG-COOK">AG Cook</a>合作。 <em>《NME》</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jonsi-shiver-review-sigur-ros-2764855">在三星级评论中</a>表示，这张唱片“具有足够的未来主义光泽和乐观的氛围，使其保持新鲜感，让你想重新投入更多。”</p><p>今年晚些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sigur-ros-announce-2024-us-tour-with-full-orchestra-3595008">Sigur Rós 将开始一场管弦乐美国巡演，</a>以支持他们最近发行的专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sigur-ros-atta-album-review-3456675">ÁTTA</a> 》，该专辑于去年发行，也是他们十年来的首张完整专辑。巡演于 9 月 19 日从底特律开始，途经芝加哥、费城和迈阿密，最后于 10 月 4 日在德克萨斯州奥斯汀结束。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fsigur-ros-tickets%2Fartist%2F806800" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到门票。</p><p>十月，乐队继“ÁTTA”之后推出了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sigur-ros-release-special-new-heimr-edition-of-new-album-atta-3514118">名为“ÁTTA Heimr Edition”的特别版本唱片</a>。</p><p> <em>NME</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sigur-ros-atta-album-review-3456675">在一篇四星评论中</a>写道，《ÁTTA》是“一张唱片，它给了 Sigur Rós 更多存在的理由，为这个冷酷无情的世界增添了一些纯粹和自然的灵魂。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sigur Rós - 宣布新的管弦乐表演" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h1YKpcjzBrM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><h3> <strong>Sigur Rós 2024 年美国巡演日期为：</strong></h3><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>19 — 密歇根州底特律，共济会大教堂剧院</strong><br /><strong>21 — 伊利诺伊州芝加哥，礼堂剧院</strong><br /><strong>23 — 宾夕法尼亚州费城，大都会艺术博物馆</strong><br /><strong>25 — 华盛顿特区，国歌</strong><br /><strong>28 — 北卡罗来纳州达勒姆，DPAC</strong><br /> <strong>30 — 佛罗里达州迈阿密，艾德丽安·阿什特中心</strong></p><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>2 — 田纳西州纳什维尔，莱曼礼堂</strong><br /><strong>4 — 德克萨斯州奥斯汀，低音音乐厅</strong></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sigur-ros-jonsi-announces-utopian-new-album-first-light-with-singles-flicker-and-cherry-blossom-3776522">Sigur Rós 的 Jónsi 宣布“乌托邦”新专辑《First Light》中的单曲《Flicker》和《Cherry Blossom》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
